"btn btn-default btn-sm btn-skinny"><i class=3D"fa fa-user-plus"></i> regis=
ter</a> now! Your help in
    stomping out Wine issues will be greatly appreciated.</p><p>There are <=
b>29,236</b> applications currently in the database,
 with <a href=3D"https://appdb.winehq.org/objectManager.php?sClass=3Dversio=
n&amp;iId=3D2739">Final Fantasy XI Online Final Fantasy XI</a> being the
top <a href=3D"https://appdb.winehq.org/votestats.php">voted</a> applicatio=
n.
</p>
